: "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862291488,45974302,2950]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=295108]jimddr[/uid] (2026-03-25 10:44):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大也还没动手吗？那我也不急，50%仓位看戏中。。。[/quote]<br/>我是说今天卖点还没到 我开盘就加了  我说了 今天机构做大局 为了自救", "lou": 1506, "content_length": 65, "reply_to": 862291488, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774406849}, {"pid": 862292161, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 10:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862291624,45974302,2950]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1353185]等爬墙的红杏[/uid] (2026-03-25 10:45):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，有没有可能以后就是这个新资金来搭台子？这个市场不能说gjd不来就不玩儿了吧。但是现在gjd就是不进来，那就得有一个新得资金起到gjd得作用来搭这个台子，玩儿这个市场吧<br/><br/>至于这个新资金，机构、外资、或者新得多方构成都有可能？？[/quote]<br/>都是  就是慢一步的资金 没有参与做局的资金。看看能进来多少吧", "lou": 1507, "content_length": 61, "reply_to": 862291624, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774406930}, {"pid": 862299164, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 11:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862298692,45974302,2957]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64289495]生鱼片是死鱼片wk[/uid] (2026-03-25 11:27):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，如果这个时候出现没人跟的情况会怎么样[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>持续放量啊 这不是有人进来换手了么  我一点都不急。", "lou": 1508, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 862298692, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774409413}, {"pid": 862315906, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 13:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862315468,45974302,2967]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143166]浪啊图图伞[/uid] (2026-03-25 13:40):[/b]<br/><br/>看起来是硬炒[s:ac:哭笑]不是主要收入[/quote]<br/>低位光纤 只是个做接头的", "lou": 1509, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 862315468, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774417482}, {"pid": 862318858, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 58, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 14:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "电力方向有点问题  小心高点", "lou": 1510, "content_length": 24, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774418943}, {"pid": 862324254, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 14:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "套很重的那种  今天尾盘或者明早可以开始减一点 保持50%-60%安全仓位。<br/>前面大跌没割肉  现在反上来你们自己看要不要保持安全一点的仓位了", "lou": 1511, "content_length": 123, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774421464}, {"pid": 862331935, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 15:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862331690,45974302,2981]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42102571]记忆一路向北[/uid] (2026-03-25 15:46):[/b]<br/><br/>怎么说？<br/>[img]./mon_202603/25/jmQ2x-6c5aZeT3cSmt-sg.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>昨天的面子果实我觉得还是产生点用处了", "lou": 1512, "content_length": 41, "reply_to": 862331690, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774424906}, {"pid": 862341030, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 153, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 16:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "提前说一声 如果明天 冲3950以上的时候 发现缩量 白线在上  我会减回50%内 安全第一<br/>这里就是做局自救 让大家进来  今天下午是缩量 证明人还没进来太多，所以今天就没回落，但是如果再拉高一点还是没人 ，那就做局失败<br/>如果明天是继续放量 那就看量，看买盘够强就可以少减 或者不减，但是除此之外都是不太对的<br/><br/>反正明天没有任何买点。", "lou": 1513, "content_length": 293, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774428963}, {"pid": 862343297, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 17:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862343028,45974302,2984]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66982010]椰果奶茶配椰果[/uid] (2026-03-25 17:11):[/b]<br/><br/>感觉被一眼看穿我的韭菜心理[s:ac:中枪]<br/>周一割，周二周三踏空，周四忍不住进场，然后继续被割[s:ac:哭1][/quote]<br/>反正明天肯定有很多3950之后在冲的那一下进来的人<br/>这些人大概率是被割的那种 我明天算一下告诉你们有多少这种人", "lou": 1514, "content_length": 107, "reply_to": 862343028, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774430034}, {"pid": 862346512, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 64, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 17:41", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862345552,45974302,2985]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1890271]坚强的小p孩[/uid] (2026-03-25 17:32):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 光伏设备这个板块k线是不是揉搓线？[/quote]<br/>这里别揉搓了  你能看到漂亮的图都是画出来的。别问我为什么懂 我也在画", "lou": 1515, "content_length": 69, "reply_to": 862345552, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774431682}, {"pid": 862347292, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-25 17:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862346884,45974302,2985]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-03-25 17:44):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，要这么说的话，下午拉券商的也是机构资金吧<br/>估计明天也有很多这种线[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>反正目前没见GJD的主动资金。", "lou": 1516, "content_length": 32, "reply_to": 862346884, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774432107}, {"pid": 862394650, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-26 08:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862393819,45974302,2990]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42680170]你看看你？[/uid] (2026-03-26 08:40):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202603/26/jmQ2x-7ti1K15T3cSw3-5z.jpg[/img]<br/>0326期货持仓[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202603/26/jmQ2x-ld03K13T3cSwt-6m.jpg[/img]<br/>统一一下  以后看这俩 然后不断随交割日切换就行了", "lou": 1517, "content_length": 87, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202603/26/jmQ2x-ld03K13T3cSwt-6m.jpg", "size": 39, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202603/26", "name": "jmQ2x-ld03K13T3cSwt-6m.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "120"}], "reply_to": 862393819, "from_client"